subSubSection.paragraph:
Collophore (
Figs 8A–C
). Anterior side with about 23 ciliate chaetae, 3 latero-proximal, about 17 of different sizes widely distributed on tube and 3 distal mac; posterior side with numerous ciliate chaetae, proximal region with 4 elongated (1 basal unpaired) chaetae apically acuminate and distally with 1 smooth chaeta; lateral flap with 11–13 chaetae, 7 smooth and 4–6 ciliate.

